[metadata]
Name:Valley Floodcaller PumpAll trigger on noncreature spell
Goal:Win
Turns:3
Difficulty:Easy
Description:Valley Floodcaller (Otter Wizard 2/2 with Flash) is on the battlefield alongside Otter-Penguin (1/1 Otter). Casting Lightning Bolt (a noncreature instant) fires the SpellCast trigger, which pumps all Birds/Frogs/Otters/Rats you control +1/+1 until end of turn and untaps them. Valley Floodcaller (2/2 Otter Wizard) becomes 3/3 and Otter-Penguin becomes 2/2. Verifies PumpAll fires correctly with valid Otter targets present (mtg-881 wave4).

